# Quotation Automation System — VPS Deployment Rules

## ⚠️ CRITICAL: Correct VPS Identity

This project (Quotation Automation System) deploys to **ONE** VPS.
Infrastructure details (IP, SSH key path, repo path, dashboard URL) are stored in the local `.env` file and are **not committed** to this repository.

## ✅ MANDATORY CHECK BEFORE ANY SSH COMMAND

Before running ANY SSH command, you MUST verify:
1. The target IP is the correct VPS for this project (check `.env` or local notes)
2. The SSH key matches the one configured for this project
3. Never use SSH credentials from other projects

## 🔐 SSH Command Template

```bash
ssh -i ~/.ssh/<your-key> root@<your-vps-ip> "<command>"
```
